nternal SDKs to standardize integration patterns — directly aligning with Tower Loan's need for payment platform integrations and document management workflows. Together, these roles have prepared me to design, develop, and maintain scalable backend services, refactor legacy components into modern APIs, and build robust integrations across internal and third-party platforms.

